    "description": "<strong>Hero Guider</strong> 是一个建造类解谜游戏。在游戏中，玩家可以建造各种设施连接道路，从而帮助英雄通过重重迷宫。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >使用有限的资源连接道路</h2>每一个关卡有一些数量有限的用于建造的资源。玩家需要使用这些有限的资源，将道路连接起来，使得英雄可以穿过迷宫。不用惧怕犯错，你可以尝试无数次直到成功。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083520/extras/f1af1a9897795a3cd9248010e3e1e7ec.poster.avif?t=1726728759\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083520/extras/f1af1a9897795a3cd9248010e3e1e7ec.webm?t=1726728759\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083520/extras/f1af1a9897795a3cd9248010e3e1e7ec.mp4?t=1726728759\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >利用各种机关</h2>游戏中有许多有趣的机关——玩家可以通过跳板越过障碍，在传送门间穿梭……等等。赶紧进入游戏探索更多内容吧！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083520/extras/5758737012c0979e02dfc3b819db3128.poster.avif?t=1726728759\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083520/extras/5758737012c0979e02dfc3b819db3128.webm?t=1726728759\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083520/extras/5758737012c0979e02dfc3b819db3128.mp4?t=1726728759\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083520/extras/cd7cd44a34eaed7701e4c324f39f7ab9.poster.avif?t=1726728759\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083520/extras/cd7cd44a34eaed7701e4c324f39f7ab9.webm?t=1726728759\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083520/extras/cd7cd44a34eaed7701e4c324f39f7ab9.mp4?t=1726728759\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >50个待解决的谜题</h2>有50个从易到难的谜题等待解决。最开始的几个谜题在引导下很容易解决，随着游戏进度推进，这些谜题将变得越来越具有挑战性！",
